# messaging-service — layout (routes, controllers, data, utils)

- **`src/routes/*.ts`:** **`Router`** wiring only — **paths**, **middleware order**, delegation to **`controllers/`**.
- **`src/controllers/*.ts`:** **One file per route file** (`routes/auth.ts` ↔ `controllers/auth.ts`). **`RequestHandler`** factories **`(env) => …`** when **`Env`** is required.
- **`src/data/`:** MongoDB repos, Redis/RabbitMQ/S3 adapters, aggregates (**`conversations/`**, **`messages/`**, **`users/`**, …).
- **`src/utils/`:** Auth helpers, email, logger, readiness, Swagger, Socket.IO (**`realtime/`**), shared rate-limit helpers, **`types/`** (e.g. Express augmentation).
- See **`docs/PROJECT_PLAN.md` §14.1.3** (Express / HTTP services).
